_json.gridTitle: khumbh hara dhania recipe | mushroom hara dhania | healthy mushroom and coriander sabzi
_json.description: Mushrooms are called khumb in hindi. They are mildly flavoured vegetables that absorb other flavours beautifully to make a tempting dish each time. Whether it is with tomatoes and oregano or spinach, onions and garlic, they make a delectable dish in all combinations. Khumbh Hara Dhania is mildly flavoured with coriander and an array of delicate spices to create a lip smacking dish that is rich in protein, calcium and vitamin A.
